{"tid":804599,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"稱中共是匪　廈大學者遭解僱","createTime":"2018-09-03T06:48:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-03T07:42:41.000Z","uid":25558,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"30338546ba5c0c8037556e49cd95546f9bb5315e","tid":804599,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T06:48:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180903/20490716\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180903%2F20490716&d=B77mozuHgSHAw5Nhb0exGpUc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=484557d2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180903%2F20490716&h=3da939cb\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180903/20490716</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年09月03日 <br />\n<br />\n稱中共是匪　廈大學者遭解僱<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180903/large/03cf07p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180903%2Flarge%2F03cf07p.jpg&h=d31f3b53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n內地高等院校加強言禁，再有學者發表敏感言論後被炒。福建廈門大學年輕學者周運中（圖）在網上狠批中共是匪後，前日被校方解除教職，成為廈大三個月內第二名因觸碰中共言論禁區而被開除的學者。<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180903/large/a1804a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180903%2Flarge%2Fa1804a.gif&h=854bd220&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「中國人是劣等民族」<br />\n<br />\n現年34歲的周運中，上海復旦大學博士畢業，是內地年輕中國史專家，著有《鄭和下西洋新考》、《正說台灣古史》等，被炒前是廈大人文學院歷史系助理教授。周亦以「東海道子」身份在微博月旦時事，發表據報如「中國人最高境界是說假話、做假賬、訂假合同。真是最劣等民族」等言論。<br />\n<br />\n廈門大學前日發表聲明，批評周以東海道子之名在微博發表「錯誤言論，歪曲歷史事實，損害黨和國家形象，傷害國人感情」，校方決定解除周的教職。廈門大學嘉庚學院國際貿易教授尤盛東早前被指在課堂上發表政治言論，6月遭校方解約，數以百計學生網上聯署支持尤盛東。<br />\n<br />\n此外，廈大前日表示研究生田佳良今年4月批評遊客在上海迪士尼樂園亂拋垃圾，發帖辱罵對方「惡臭你支（那）」後，又被揭發在遼寧師範大學修讀本科課程期間發表論文存在不當行為，校方因此勒令田佳良退學。<br />\n<br />\n微博  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n教育節目狂播12分鐘廣告<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n劉強東涉性侵被美警拘捕<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n教育資源不足　學位短缺<br />\n<br />\n教育節目狂播12分鐘廣告<br />\n<br />\n抗議湖南公校不足爆騷亂　二萬私校家長遭鎮壓"},{"pid":"7dfd5b65de34edddee503fee1350e7e07acf0969","tid":804599,"uid":35014,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T06:59:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"04336ce3c0e218eda07b5a6e949895ca24e8d1e7","tid":804599,"uid":104443,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T07:16:02.000Z","msg":"讀歷史真係唔同啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e4511ed0773c06f46776763a16ed67a00c56db6","tid":804599,"uid":49588,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"04336ce3c0e218eda07b5a6e949895ca24e8d1e7","tid":804599,"uid":104443,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T07:16:02.000Z","msg":"讀歷史真係唔同啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T07:19:07.000Z","msg":"只要讀過真實歷史，就知道共是匪！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以土匪不斷修改歷史中⋯"},{"pid":"43d7192a8747e1ddd13e141e9a875a6f4d52d688","tid":804599,"uid":122850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T07:19:59.000Z","msg":"係咪連登仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1eecf161fba7d1538215f969b9046d0cf3d4c751","tid":804599,"uid":15730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T07:20:23.000Z","msg":"Fucking u<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef60f420d8cb174d890b22d785816b90d10d7829","tid":804599,"uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T07:20:31.000Z","msg":"垃圾國家"},{"pid":"5247de4874ea4d903552bc83b2fbc1a21a36e69e","tid":804599,"uid":106247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0